title: IP-1 - URN to mint additional NFTs
body:
Proposal:

URN Mints NFTs to finalize OTC deal.

Issue:

During the sale of The Internship, URN agreed to an OTC deal, to raise funds for Merge. URN decided to sell 90 NFTs to Pranksy. 

Pranksy sent URN 12.03 ETH in return for 90 Internship NFTs. URN did not complete the transaction and burned the remaining unsold NFTs at the end of the sale in error. 

Solution:

URN mints 90 NFTs to complete the transaction with Pranksy.
